      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4とはいえ、お互いに忙し過ぎた……\nでも、今日こそテーマ作りを進めよう……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.6614956062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "うん。まずは二人でアイデアを出し合っていこっか\nそこから良さそうなものを選ぶ感じで――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1648276171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.3448272547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "ホラーにアイドル好き……\n私達らしいアイデアを沢山出せたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.5627419314
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、ここからテーマを決めるのは、結構大変そう\n細かいアイデアがあるのはいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.800701062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。すずちゃんと芽衣ちゃんの曲作りを参考に\nお互いの『好き』を詰め込んでみたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.995122703
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと出し過ぎたかも……？\n細かいアイデアもいいけど、もっと大きな枠が必要かも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6672313215
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "一度、視点を変えてみてもいいかもしれないね\n例えば……私達の関係性について考えてみる、とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.4447149438
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "二人の関係性……ドルオタ的にも胸アツな言葉\nライブやMVで、エモい演出が出来そうで最高",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.5113814197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "何か、新しいアイデアが出そうな予感……\nふわぁ……ごめん、あくびが出ちゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9580476287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……。えへへ、私も……\n今日も忙しかったから、眠たくなってきちゃったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4333319027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.9553946658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "アイデアは沢山出せたし、今日はそろそろ寝よっか？\n千紗ちゃん、明日は朝からお仕事だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.1320612752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "うん……ごめんね？　せっかくデュエットの相手に\n選んでくれたのに、なかなか進められなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9602015659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku Hyodo",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_12_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "ううん。千紗ちゃんと一緒だったから\n沢山アイデアを出せた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2666652361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
